A group of mostly female intergalactic space pirates pulls off a major heist aboard a casino ship. The law is close on their tail and their only option is a moon planet where they have to make a crash landing. A strange force quickly takes over the captain's body and she disappears. The remaining crew reluctantly teams up with the law when they realize that they are being picked off one by one and turning into undead bloodsuckers.
